Class CallGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FEReplacer
      • sketch.compiler.passes.structure.CallGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CudaCallGraph

    public class CallGraph
extends FEReplacer
    determines which functions call which functions, and the closure. debug print code commented out in GlobalsToParams visitor (if it's not working correctly, or you want to see output).
    Author:
    gatoatigrado (nicholas tung) [email: ntung at ntung]
